{{vgname|狙击精英4|en=Sniper Elite 4|tw=狙擊之神4|cn=狙击精英4}}是一款由[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]]開發与发行的[[第三人稱遊戲|第三人稱]][[隱蔽類遊戲|隱蔽類]][[戰術射擊遊戲|戰術射擊遊戲]]，为《[[狙击精英III|狙击精英III]]》續作。遊戲於2017年2月14日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]及[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台發行，后于2020年11月登陆[[Google_Stadia|Stadia]]和[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]。

== 游戏玩法 ==
[[File:Sniper_Elite_4_Killcam.jpg|left]]
《狙击精英4》是一款具有[[隐蔽类游戏|潜行]]元素的[[第三人称游戏|第三人称]][[战术射击游戏|战术射击游戏]]。当玩家在远距离使用狙击步枪杀死敌人时，X射线击杀特写系统将被激活，游戏镜头会跟随子弹一直到击中目标，显示身体部分、骨骼或内部身体器官被子弹打破的情形<ref name="GIRev">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/sniper_elite_4/b/pc/archive/2016/03/17/our-first-look-at-sniper-elite-4s-blood-gushing-bone-breaking-action.aspx|title=Our First Look At Sniper Elite 4's Blood-Gushing, Bone-Breaking Action|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-17|last=Futter|first=Mike|publisher=[[GameStop|GameStop]]|website=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|archive-date=2018-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109212635/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/sniper_elite_4/b/pc/archive/2016/03/17/our-first-look-at-sniper-elite-4s-blood-gushing-bone-breaking-action.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该系统还扩展到弹片消灭、近战消灭和隐身消灭<ref name="EuroGPre">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-03-16-sniper-elite-4-brings-a-little-more-polish-and-a-lot-more-scale-to-the-series|title=Sniper Elite 4 brings a little more polish and a lot more scale to the series|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-16|last=Robinson|first=Martin|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Gamer Network]]|website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118175658/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-03-16-sniper-elite-4-brings-a-little-more-polish-and-a-lot-more-scale-to-the-series|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

游戏的[[人工智能|人工智能]]得到改进，敌人能更灵活地对玩家的行动做出反应。当有敌人被杀死时，其他人会开始积极寻找<ref name="DSPreview">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/feature/a787284/sniper-elite-4-review-preview-gameplay-xbox-one-ps4-pc/|title=Sniper Elite 4 preview: 4 reasons it's better than ever|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-19|last=Loveridge|first=Sam|publisher=[[赫斯特国际集团|Hearst Magazines UK]]|website=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|archive-date=2018-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104102822/http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/feature/a787284/sniper-elite-4-review-preview-gameplay-xbox-one-ps4-pc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩家配备一副双筒望远镜，可以显示敌人的位置以及武器配备。 游戏中有一个“军官”排名。 尽快杀死军官会使其军队撤退，而在任务结束时杀死他会大大增加游戏难度<ref name="DSPreview" />。玩家可以放置陷阱以及使用尸体[[詭雷|诡雷]]<ref name="GReactor">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamereactor.eu/news/403853/Rebellion+on+making+Sniper+Elite+4+a+snipers+paradise/|title=Rebellion on making Sniper Elite 4 "a sniper's paradise"|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-30|last=Holmes|first=Mike|website=[[Gamereactor|Gamereactor]]|archive-date=2018-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124162947/https://www.gamereactor.eu/news/403853/Rebellion+on+making+Sniper+Elite+4+a+snipers+paradise/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏还有夜间任务，玩家可以设法关闭光源隐藏自己<ref name="GIRev" /><ref name="DSPreview" />。

游戏地图比前作要大得多，玩家有更多的自由与开放式游戏体验<ref name="EuroGPre" />。地图还有更多的垂直性。 游戏的新运动系统令玩家可以攀爬与抓住窗台<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.destructoid.com/sniper-elite-4-now-with-more-assassin-s-creed-349638.phtml|title=Sniper Elite 4, now with more Assassin's Creed|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-19|last=Makedonski|first=Brett|publisher=[[Destructoid|ModernMethod]]|website=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411001459/https://www.destructoid.com/sniper-elite-4-now-with-more-assassin-s-creed-349638.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[合作游戏模式|合作任务]]与多人竞争模式重新加入游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/3/7/11172650/sniper-elite-4-announced-launch-date-pc-ps4-xbox-one|title=Sniper Elite 4 sends the World War II series to Italy this year|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-05-07|last=Good|first=Owen S.|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140040/http://www.polygon.com/2016/3/7/11172650/sniper-elite-4-announced-launch-date-pc-ps4-xbox-one|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==
《狙击精英4》的故事发生在1943年的意大利，紧随《狙击精英III》的事件。玩家控制[[特别行动执行处|SOE]]特工卡尔·费尔伯恩（Karl Fairburne），在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]中协助{{le|意大利抵抗运动|Italian resistance movement|意大利游击队}}与[[法西斯意大利_(1922年－1943年)|法西斯義大利]]作战，並阻止[[納粹德國|納粹德國]]部署導彈以協助盟軍登陸意大利。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/03/07/sniper-elite-4-launching-this-year|title=Sniper Elite 4 Launching This Year|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-07|last=Carpenter|first=Nicole|publisher=[[IGN|IGN Entertainment]]|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091846/https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/03/07/sniper-elite-4-launching-this-year|dead-url=no}}</ref>

故事开篇，[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]派出调查纳粹新武器传言的货轮在意大利西南圣瑟里尼（San Celini）岛附近被德军无线电制导反舰导弹击沉，卡尔受命登岛暗杀监督导弹袭击宣传片拍摄的托拜厄斯·施密特（Tobias Schmidt）将军并取得情报。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务1 圣瑟里尼岛}}</ref>消灭施密特后，卡尔得知导弹由火箭科学家安德烈亚斯·凯斯勒（Andreas Kessler）设计研发，[[战略情报局|OSS]]的情报显示其就在意大利，受神秘的纳粹德国将军海因茨·博姆（Heinz Böhm）保护。与卡尔在毕坦提（Bitanti）村接头的OSS特工杰克·韦弗（Jack Weaver）请他帮忙联络上了当地意大利游击队领袖“天使”索菲亚·迪洛克（Sofia "Angel" Di Rocco）。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务2 毕坦提村}}</ref>但由于OSS在其父被纳粹绑架时袖手旁观，索菲亚最初并不信任卡尔，要求他摧毁雷基利诺[[高架桥|高架桥]]（Regelino Viaduct）上的[[列车炮|列车炮]]证明合作诚意。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务3 雷基利诺高架桥}}</ref>

完成了索菲亚的委托，卡尔又潜入纳粹运输导弹部件的造船厂，查明位置后引导[[盟军|盟军]]轰炸机将货物尽数炸毁。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务4 洛里诺造船厂}}</ref>期间他获悉[[西西里黑手党|西西里黑手党]]同样在此干扰纳粹行动，于是被安排与黑手党领袖塞尔瓦托·迪内利（Salvatore Dinelli）会面以争取后者支持，迪内利则开出消灭{{le|黑色旅|Black Brigades}}头目皮耶罗·卡波（Piero Capo）的条件。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务5 阿布鲁齐修道院}}</ref>盟军与黑手党合作令游击队颇为反感，此时韦弗的线人汉斯·多夫曼（Hans Dorfmann）少校突然找到卡尔，透露凯斯勒藏身于纳粹组装导弹的玛咖泽诺设施（Magazzeno Facility），卡尔遂潜入设施绑回凯斯勒。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务6 玛咖泽诺设施}}</ref>凯斯勒于受审时表示索菲亚之父就关在吉奥维菲奥里尼（Giovi Fiorini）镇，诱导游击队前去攻打，其实他自知罹患[[肝癌|肝癌]]时日无多，才编造谎言引游击队自投罗网。卡尔赶去解决了博姆的亲信，但为时已晚，游击队员惨遭屠戮殆尽。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务7 吉奥维菲奥里尼大楼}}</ref>

从其亲信身上取得的情报表明博姆早已知悉盟军登陆意大利本土的{{le|雪崩行动|Operation Avalanche}}，并计划从阿拉伽拉（Allagra）堡垒发射新型导弹击沉[[德怀特·艾森豪威尔|德怀特·艾森豪威尔]]所在的指挥舰。卡尔潜入堡垒破坏了所有导弹，此时多夫曼突然携被俘的索菲亚出现，表明他就是博姆。关键时刻索菲亚牺牲自己助卡尔逃出包围，博姆则意欲乘飞机离开。最终卡尔在其起飞前击毁引擎结果了博姆，又指引盟军轰炸机摧毁整个基地。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=任务8 阿拉伽拉堡垒}}</ref>结尾卡尔和韦弗再度相遇，并被邀请为OSS效力。<ref>{{cite video game|title=Sniper Elite 4 |developer=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |publisher=[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]] |date=2017-02-14|scene=终曲}}</ref>

== 开发 ==
《狙击精英4》由[[Rebellion_Developments|Rebellion Developments]]开发。 根据Rebellion创意总监蒂姆·琼斯（Tim Jones）的说法，游戏被设计为“狙击天堂”<ref name="GReactor" />。团队扩大了游戏地图与关卡的大小规模，使得“真正的远距离射击”成为可能 。 动画系统、人工智能和游戏的[[渲染|渲染]]技术也进行了重新设计<ref name="GReactor" />。由于技术限制，游戏不会在[[第七代游戏机|第七代游戏机]]平台发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/ww2-sniper-elite-4-coming-this-year-to-xbox-one-an/1100-6435418/|title=WW2 Sniper Elite 4 Coming This Year to Xbox One and PS4 With 1080p Graphics|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-07|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103013/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ww2-sniper-elite-4-coming-this-year-to-xbox-one-an/1100-6435418/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

前两款游戏的发行商[[505游戏|505游戏]]不再参与游戏制作，《狙击精英4》将由Rebellion自行发布数字版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/sniper_elite_4/news/sniper_elite_4_is_set_in_ww2_italy_coming_to_ps4_xbox_one_and_pc_in_2016.html|title=Sniper Elite 4 is set in WW2 Italy, coming to PS4, Xbox One & PC in 2016|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-07|last=Scammell|first=David|publisher=[[VideoGamer.com|Candy Banana]]|website=[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]|archive-date=2016-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801164812/http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/sniper_elite_4/news/sniper_elite_4_is_set_in_ww2_italy_coming_to_ps4_xbox_one_and_pc_in_2016.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Rebellion与《僵尸部队三部曲》的出版商与分销商Sold Out和U＆I Entertainment合作，制作游戏的实体版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2016/03/14/sniper-elite-4-is-getting-a-physical-release/197823/|title='Sniper Elite 4' is Getting a Physical Release|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-14|last=Dang|first=Edward|website=[[Hardcore_Gamer|Hardcore Gamer]]|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911213036/https://www.hardcoregamer.com/2016/03/14/sniper-elite-4-is-getting-a-physical-release/197823/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年2月，一家中国数字艺术公司意外泄漏该游戏。Rebellion首席执行官詹森·金斯利（Jason Kingsley）没有证实此事，并补充道他们很快会公开一个新游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/sniper_elite_3/news/sniper_elite_4_outed_by_linkedin_profile.html|title=Sniper Elite 4 outed by LinkedIn profile|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-02-15|last=Scammell|first=David|publisher=[[VideoGamer.com|Candy Banana]]|website=[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701161221/http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/sniper_elite_3/news/sniper_elite_4_outed_by_linkedin_profile.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《狙击精英4》于2016年3月7日公布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/sniper-elite-4-has-2016-release-in-its-sights/|title=Sniper Elite 4 has 2016 release in its sights|accessdate=2016-06-03|date=2016-03-07|last=Morrison|first=Angus|publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]]|website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120013205/https://www.pcgamer.com/sniper-elite-4-has-2016-release-in-its-sights/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年6月13日，在[[E3_2016|E3 2016]]上Rebellion宣布《狙击精英4》将于2017年2月14日发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/sniper-elite-4-delayed-to-2017-see-new-brutal-scre/1100-6440808/|title=Sniper Elite 4 Delayed to 2017, See New Brutal Screenshots Here|accessdate=2016-06-14|date=2016-06-13|last=Paget|first=Mat|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2016-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616122427/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/sniper-elite-4-delayed-to-2017-see-new-brutal-scre/1100-6440808/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

